    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8086-b5cf-d3e27d1d7157",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Recommender Systems can be used to help students select courses who are better suited for them. Paper suggests a hybrid RS that combines both Content-Based Filtering and Collaborative Filtering.  Optimization of the parameters of the Recommender System is done via a Genetic Algorithm.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8086-b5cf-d3e27d1d7157",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
