    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-8092-990c-fbb0754e9d87",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "An experiemntal sewtup on the university of Cordoba, a dataset with 2500 entries with 95 students and 63 courses. Results show excellent performance of recommendations in comparison to previous models. Moreover, the authors also delve into the interpretation of the most relevant criteria for course recommendation.",
